</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>System » Settings » Editors</strong> and determine which editors should be available for certain areas in your plentymarkets system. Choose between <strong>Editor</strong>, <strong>Syntax editor</strong> and <strong>Text field</strong>.</p>
