<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>New order from online store</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The customers receive an email including the order confirmation after the purchase has been completed in the online store.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Send customer email to change password</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The customers receive an email with a link to the new password. The link must be actively confirmed. The template function <strong>&#123;&#37; Link_ChangePassword() &#37;&#125;</strong> must be included in the email template.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Newsletter opt-in</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The customers receive an email when they have registered for the newsletter. The email template should include the confirmation link that the customers have to click in order to complete the newsletter registration process.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
